author: Warhammer
description:
Brutal & Cunning is here, and with it the awesome new plastic Ratlings! Ollie has been super excited awaiting these models, but not for the reason you may think. Tune in to see Ollie combine two of his favourite kill teams in order to create perhaps the tiniest worshippers of the dark gods we’ve ever seen… Traitor Ratlings!
